headline: Sonia Syngal Joins Tractor Supply Board As Valuation And Strategy Watched
summary: Tractor Supply Company (NasdaqGS:TSCO) has appointed Sonia Syngal, former CEO of Gap Inc. and Old Navy, to its Board of Directors. Syngal brings more than 30 years of retail, e commerce, and supply chain leadership experience to the company. This Board change represents a governance update that may shape future decisions on operations and digital priorities. Tractor Supply, the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, sits at the crossroads of consumer, agricultural, and pet...

headline: Tractor Supply Kicks off 11th Annual Grants for Growing Campaign, Investing in Future Ag Leaders
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., February 18, 2026--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States (the "Company"), announced today the launch of its 11th annual Grants for Growing fundraiser on February 19, empowering FFA students nationwide with hands-on learning experiences that prepare them for careers in agriculture and skilled trades. Since 2016, Tractor Supply customers have contributed nearly $9 million to support local FFA chapters. Timed to celebrate
